data.description: Brick Rancher home in Riverdale. This home has 4 bedrooms and 2 full bath with a gorgeous sunroom in the back of the house.  All bedrooms are spacious and equipped with double closets. This home provides a place for comfortable every life, great entertaining and making memories. Water heater, HVAC, and windows within 4years. Lots of great shopping, restaurants and Langley Air Force base is close. Come see for yourself!
